data.description: Welcome to 3452 Plymouth Place as you step inside, you will be greeted by an updated kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances and beautiful granite countertops. The kitchen seamlessly flows into the dining and living area, creating a perfect space for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. In addition to the main living area, this home also boasts a versatile flex space connected to the living area. This flexible space can be customized to suit your needs, whether it be a home office, playroom, or even a cozy reading place. Downstairs, you will find a convenient full bath along with two bedrooms. As you head upstairs to your primary bedroom and bath you will be amazed by the ample space for relaxation and comfort. Another bedroom is also situated upstairs, accompanied by the third full bathroom right down the hall! For added convenience, this house includes a detached garage and a fenced-in backyard. The covered patio allows you to enjoy outdoor activities. Located in the desirable neighborhood of Aurora Gardens, this property offers easy access to nearby amenities such as shopping centers, restaurants, and outdoor activities. Whether you prefer to spend your weekends exploring or indulging in retail therapy, there is something for everyone just moments away. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your new home. Plumbing was replaced in 2020, AC System replaced in 2020, and a Brand New Roof was installed last week.
